title: Replace all Python scripts with Tcl scripts.
date: Sun Feb  7 13:43:13 EST 2010

It would probably best not to require both Python and Tcl, and, since
the plan is to use Tcl to glue modules together in the game itself, Tcl
seems like the logical choice.  Also, it's a much nicer language than Python
in many ways.
